      "value": "<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Traditions </strong>Divine, Occult</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Access </strong>sea horse</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Cast </strong>[two-actions] somatic, verbal</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Range</strong> 30 feet; <strong>Area </strong>30 foot diameter sphere</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Duration </strong>1 minute</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"> </p>\n<hr />\n<p> </p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Any effect with the auditory or linguistic trait that attempts to work in the affected area is hampered. Its DC is lowered by 2 and if it deals dice of damage, it deals 2 less dice of damage.</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"> </p>\n<hr />\n<p> </p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Heightened (+1) The DC is lowered by 1 more and it deals 1 less die of damage.</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"> </p>"
